arguments for running

--without arguments
menu based simulator program will running

--one argument(file name)
will run the program on all type of architecture with no steps printed.

--with two or three argment

first argument is file name 
second argument is 0 for single cycle , 1 for Mips simulator, 3 for r4000 Mips simulator
third argument is to print each and every step to a file steps.txt
